Khanna, the provocative Silicon Valley congressman, on how the Democratic P=
arty fumbled its connection with the American working class, what Barack Ob=
ama got right and Joe Biden got wrong, why he=E2=80=99s open to working wit=
h Elon Musk, and why Trump-voting towns and counties ravaged by NAFTA must =
be saved. And oh yeah, I asked if he wants to run for president, too.

